    • addSensorToRoom

      public void addSensorToRoom(String name, String room, String sensorType)
      Adds sensor to a room; 1. Checks if the room exists in the list of rooms; 2. Checks if the sensor type is permitted; 3. Checks if the specific room contains a sensor with the same name with @addSensorToRoom; 4. Adds the sensor to the list of sensors in the instantiation of room;
      Parameters:
      name - Name
      room - Room
      sensorType - Sensor type

    • addSensorType

      public void addSensorType(String sensorType)
      Adds a sensor type to the list of available sensor types. 1. Verifies the sensor type is permitted in the system (using @getTypeOfSensor); 2. Creates a new sensor type; 3. Adds sensor type to the list of sensor types;
      Parameters:
      sensorType - Sensor type
